  "page": {
    "documentTitle": "基準率忽略 | Concept Reading Lab",
    "bodyClass": "knowledge-page knowledge-base-rate-neglect",
    "heroHtml": "<div class=\"hero-inner\">\n  <div>\n    <p class=\"kicker\">Knowledge Study / probability / bias / evidence</p>\n    <h1>基準率忽略</h1>\n    <p class=\"topic-subtitle\">Base Rate Neglect</p>\n    <p class=\"thesis\">當個案敘事很鮮明時，人會把整體分布忘掉，讓判斷看起來像在讀證據，其實是在追故事。</p>\n    <div class=\"hero-prompt\">\n      <strong>Read For</strong>\n      <p>這頁要幫你建立一個習慣：每當某個案例看起來非常像答案時，先退一步問它在母體裡到底多常見。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <aside class=\"hero-note\" aria-label=\"主題資訊\">\n    <dl class=\"lexical-meta lexical-meta--knowledge\" aria-label=\"主題摘要\">\n      <div>\n        <dt>主題類型</dt>\n        <dd>認知偏誤 / 機率判斷</dd>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <dt>核心問題</dt>\n        <dd>Prior probability vs. vivid evidence</dd>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <dt>主要判準</dt>\n        <dd>先驗分布、條件證據、樣本母體、更新規則</dd>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <dt>讀完產出</dt>\n        <dd>能把直覺判斷拆成 prior 與 case evidence</dd>\n      </div>\n    </dl>\n    <div class=\"knowledge-map\" aria-label=\"閱讀結構示意\">\n      <span>先驗</span>\n      <span>個案</span>\n      <span>更新</span>\n    </div>\n  </aside>\n</div>",
    "mainHtml": "<aside class=\"compass\" aria-label=\"頁內導覽\">\n  <span>Reading Path</span>\n  <a href=\"#core\">讀法總覽</a>\n  <a href=\"#setup\">問題設定</a>\n  <a href=\"#lenses\">判準透鏡</a>\n  <a href=\"#psychology\">心理連結</a>\n  <a href=\"#applications\">現實映射</a>\n  <a href=\"#misreadings\">誤讀校正</a>\n  <a href=\"#questions\">延伸提問</a>\n  <a href=\"#sources\">來源</a>\n</aside>\n\n<article class=\"article\">\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"core\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Orientation</p>\n      <h2>當鮮明線索壓過母體分布</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">基準率忽略不是不會算數，而是大腦太容易被具體故事吸走，導致分布資訊在關鍵時刻被邊緣化。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"core-card\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Core Tension</p>\n      <p>個案細節讓你覺得自己抓到了真相，但沒有 base rate 的故事，只是在沒有底圖的情況下放大局部線索。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"principle-strip\" aria-label=\"本頁讀法\">\n      <div>\n        <span>01</span>\n        <strong>先問母體</strong>\n        <p>在討論個案前，先說清楚事件在整體母體中的稀有程度。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <span>02</span>\n        <strong>再看證據力度</strong>\n        <p>不是每一條線索都足以推翻先驗分布，很多線索只是讓故事更像。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <span>03</span>\n        <strong>最後才更新</strong>\n        <p>判斷應該是 prior 被 evidence 修正，而不是被單一案例直接取代。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"setup\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Setup</p>\n      <h2>把問題縮到最小</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">這個偏誤最常出現在你覺得自己很重視證據的時候，因為個案線索往往比抽象比率更有存在感。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"definition-grid\">\n      <div class=\"tile\">\n        <strong>最小劇情</strong>\n        <p>某人看到一個看起來很像資安入侵的異常封包，於是立刻判斷系統已被攻破，卻沒先問該型態在正常流量裡本來就有多常見。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"tile\">\n        <strong>真正難點</strong>\n        <p>只要案例描述夠具體，人的直覺就會覺得它比冷冰冰的母體比例更可靠，哪怕兩者其實應該一起看。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"concept-flow\" aria-label=\"問題展開\">\n      <div class=\"flow-step\">個案細節很鮮明</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-arrow\">→</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-step\">整體分布被忘掉</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-arrow\">→</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-step\">低機率事件被誤判成高機率</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"paradox-frame\">\n      <strong>Key Point</strong>\n      <p>基準率忽略最危險的地方，不是算錯，而是把代表性的感覺誤當成真正的機率更新。</p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"lenses\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Lenses</p>\n      <h2>三個拆解這個偏誤的角度</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">如果你想避免被個案帶著走，可以把判斷拆成三層：母體、證據、更新幅度。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"lens-grid\">\n      <article class=\"lens-card\">\n        <strong>母體分布</strong>\n        <p>先問事件本來有多常見。罕見事件需要更強的證據才值得大幅改判。</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"lens-card\">\n        <strong>證據品質</strong>\n        <p>線索到底是真正區分度高，還是只是語意上看起來很像答案。</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"lens-card\">\n        <strong>更新幅度</strong>\n        <p>好的判斷不是全有全無，而是根據證據強弱逐步調整信心。</p>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"table-wrap\">\n      <table>\n        <thead>\n          <tr>\n            <th>看法</th>\n            <th>看起來像</th>\n            <th>真正風險</th>\n          </tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n          <tr>\n            <td>只看個案像不像</td>\n            <td>直覺很有把握</td>\n            <td>稀有但吸睛的解釋被過度高估。</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>先看基準率</td>\n            <td>判斷沒那麼戲劇化</td>\n            <td>若證據真的很強，仍要允許大幅更新。</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>把兩者一起算</td>\n            <td>思路比較慢</td>\n            <td>需要紀律，但能避免把故事錯當分布。</td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"psychology\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Psychology</p>\n      <h2>為什麼個案故事總比基準率更有說服力</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">人比較容易記住臉、事件與情節，不容易記住抽象的分母，所以 base rate 常在心理上先輸一半。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"example-grid\">\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>故事比比例更抓人</strong>\n        <p>一個具體案例會讓人感到自己正在接觸真相，分布資料則常被誤認成抽象背景噪音。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>代表性會冒充機率</strong>\n        <p>只要某個案例很像你心中的典型，大腦就會把像不像直接轉譯成多不多。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"micro-note\">重點不是要求每次都手算 Bayes，而是提醒你不要讓 vivid cue 直接霸占判斷。</p>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"applications\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Applications</p>\n      <h2>把先驗機率放回告警與診斷</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">在工程與產品現場，這個偏誤常出現在 debug、告警解讀、異常分流與風險評估。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"example-grid\">\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>異常告警判讀</strong>\n        <p>某個指標長得像攻擊、不代表最可能是攻擊；若誤報本來很多，就不能直接把單次命中當定案。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>Field issue 分流</strong>\n        <p>看到兩台機器同時出現同一症狀，直覺會想成 systemic bug，但也要先看該症狀在正常使用裡本來就多不多。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <ul class=\"bullet-list\">\n      <li>遇到強烈個案時，先補一句：這件事在母體裡有多常見？</li>\n      <li>把判斷寫成「先驗 + 證據 + 更新」，比直接喊結論更不容易失真。</li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"misreadings\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Misreadings</p>\n      <h2>別把它縮成一句「學 Bayes 就好」</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">很多人知道要看證據，卻忘了沒有 base rate 的證據其實缺了一半脈絡。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"collocation-list\" aria-label=\"常見誤讀\">\n      <article class=\"collocation-card\">\n        <div>\n          <strong>所以只要看基準率</strong>\n          <span class=\"register-tag\">校正</span>\n        </div>\n        <p>不是。基準率提供底圖，但強證據仍然能大幅修正判斷。</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"collocation-card\">\n        <div>\n          <strong>只有統計人才會遇到</strong>\n          <span class=\"register-tag\">校正</span>\n        </div>\n        <p>任何需要分辨常見噪音與罕見真因的工作，都在跟這個偏誤打交道。</p>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"questions\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Questions</p>\n      <h2>用兩個提問把分布請回桌上</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">下面兩個問題，適合在看到非常像答案的案例時先拿來踩煞車。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"prompt-grid\">\n      <article class=\"prompt-card\">\n        <strong>如果這類事件其實很罕見</strong>\n        <p>你現在手上的證據，真的強到足以推翻低基準率，還是只是敘事上很有代表性？</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"prompt-card\">\n        <strong>如果把分母補回來</strong>\n        <p>你是否還會做同樣判斷，還是信心其實應該比直覺低很多？</p>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"template-note\">\n      <strong>延伸路線</strong>\n      <p>延伸閱讀可看 Bayes、representativeness heuristic、false positive paradox；也可以把這一頁帶回告警系統與診斷流程設計。</p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"sources\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Sources</p>\n      <h2>來源與整理方式</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">核心概念來自認知偏誤與機率更新的討論；文中的工程例子則沿著這些框架做的教學性轉譯。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"source-grid\">\n      <article class=\"source-card\">\n        <strong>主概念</strong>\n        <p>Base rate fallacy 條目整理了基準率忽略的標準定義與常見例子。</p>\n        <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Base_rate_fallacy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Base rate fallacy</a>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"source-card\">\n        <strong>更新框架</strong>\n        <p>Bayes' theorem 提供了把先驗分布與新證據結合的最基本形式。</p>\n        <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bayes%27_theorem\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Bayes' theorem</a>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"source-card\">\n        <strong>相鄰偏誤</strong>\n        <p>Representativeness heuristic 說明人為何容易把像不像當成機率高低。</p>\n        <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Representativeness_heuristic\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Representativeness heuristic</a>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\">\n    <div class=\"reference-box\">\n      <div>\n        <p class=\"section-label\">Reference</p>\n        <h2>下一步</h2>\n        <p>如果這個主題讀起來有用，下一步很適合補一頁談 false positive 與 decision threshold，讓 debug 與檢測流程更完整。</p>\n      </div>\n      <a class=\"reference-link\" href=\"../knowledge-topic-template.html\">打開模板</a>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</article>"
  }
}
